BuildConflicts: openmcl-64bit (<= 1.0-1), gmp-64bit (<= 4.2.1-1005), gmp-64bit-shlibs (<= 4.2.1-1005), libgmpxx4-64bit-shlibs (<= 4.2.1-1005)
